Introduction

SONAMOO (also stylized as sonΛmoo) was a seven-member girl group formed by TS Entertainment. They debuted on December 29, 2014 with the mini album "Deja Vu".

TS Entertainment shut down on early 2021. After all members signed with new companies by the end of 2021 and the group was silently disbanded.
